SAP Basis/Portal Consultant
SAP Basis/Portal Consultant
Location:  Singapore
SAP Basis/Portal Consultant- Permanent- Singapore
Job Responsibilities:
- Maintain and administer SAP systems
- Administer and monitor transport management system
- Involved in application installation, user and security administration as well as system optimization
- Apply patches and upgrades
- Assist in project implementation
Job Requirements:
- Degree in Computer Science/Information Technology or any equivalent qualifications
- Experience in SAP Basis with at least 2 years of experience
- Netweaver solutions are advantageous
- Only Singaporeans need apply
Please can all interested candidates forward a copy of their up to date CV to michelle.hoangcv@amoriabond.com.sg for immediate interview.
Amoria Bond operates as an employment agency and employment business.
No terminology in this advert is intended to discriminate on the grounds of age, and we confirm that we are happy to accept applications from persons of any age for this role.
